Adeniran Ogunsanya College of Education, nke a makwara dị ka AOCOED, bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ agụmakwụkwọ dị elu nke dị na obodo Oto-Awori na mpaghara Oto-Awuri nke Ojo, Steeti Lagos Adeniran Ogunsanya College of Education na-enye onyinye nke Nigeria Certificate in Education (NCE) na undergraduate mbụ degree ọmụmụ na Education, ebe ọ nwere njikọ na Ekiti State University.
E guzobere kọleji ahụ, nke a na-akpọbu Lagos State College of Education, na afọ 1958 dị ka kọleji ọzụzụ ndị nkuzi nke Grade III, na-edebanye aha ihe dị ka ụmụ akwụkwọ iri itoolu n'afọ mbụ ya
N'afọ 1982, n'ihi enweghị akụrụngwa, ihe owuwu ọgbara ọhụrụ na mmụba nke ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ, a kwagara kọleji ahụ site na Surulere gaa n'ebe ọ dị ugbu a na Oto-Awori.
